{"tid":1582124,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安倍 : 日本建立 “宇宙自衛隊” 並非夢話","createTime":"2019-09-20T01:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T07:52:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"0a79945bc2997542e4c86b181128d0aca0fbd7a7","tid":1582124,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T01:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/dynimagecache/0/0/3000/1694/1024/578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aefimagesnew/aef_image/2019-09-11t094328z_1046276220_rc1b02d6a990_rtrmadp_3_japan-politics-reshuffle_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fdynimagecache%2F0%2F0%2F3000%2F1694%2F1024%2F578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faefimagesnew%2Faef_image%2F2019-09-11t094328z_1046276220_rc1b02d6a990_rtrmadp_3_japan-politics-reshuffle_0.jpg&h=3dbcc05a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本首相安倍晉三17日上午在自衛隊高級幹部集會上訓話，他表示：明年自衛隊將建立&ldquo;宇宙作戰隊&rdquo;，而將&ldquo;宇宙作戰隊&rdquo;進化為&ldquo;宇宙自衛隊&rdquo;也並非夢想。<br />\n<br />\n日本防衛省8月30日提出了2020年度預算概算要求總額，創歷史新高。去年制定的《防衛計畫大綱》提出加強太空等安全保障新領域的應對能力，為了對應美國及中國等展開競爭的太空&ldquo;新戰場&rdquo;，將在航空自衛隊新設&ldquo;宇宙作戰隊&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n安倍首相指出：可以說，自衛隊正面臨著創設以來最大的變化，明年自衛隊將建立&ldquo;宇宙作戰隊&rdquo;，而將&ldquo;宇宙作戰隊&rdquo;進化為&ldquo;宇宙自衛隊&rdquo;也並非夢想。<br />\n<br />\n安倍首相指出：防衛大綱新導入的&ldquo;宇宙、網絡攻擊和電磁波等領域&rdquo;，會使安全保障的結構為之一變，為此各國在先進技術開發上激烈競爭，我們不應該無視這一現實，對所有的事態的發生做出準備，徹底保護國民的生命、財產，是諸位的使命。安倍首相強調了強化這些新的領域的防衛能力的必要性，要求在這些領域導入&ldquo;人工智能、省力和無人化技術，提高效率。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n安倍指出：這些新領域，&ldquo;應該說是就像與眼睛和耳朵、全身連接在一起的神經迴路一樣，能否保持優勢，直接關係到我國的防衛能力。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n安倍首相強調：自衛隊現在得到90%的國民的信任，但是他今年沒有提到去年曾經言及的修改憲法九條，明確記載自衛隊的存在的憲法修正案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2/20190917-%E5%AE%89%E5%80%8D%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%88%96%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%AE%87%E5%AE%99%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B%E9%9A%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%2F20190917-%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2580%258D%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25AE%2587%25E5%25AE%2599%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A1%259B%25E9%259A%258A&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8om5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=b8d3e8ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2/20190917-%E5%AE%89%E5%80%8D%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%88%96%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%AE%87%E5%AE%99%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B%E9%9A%8A</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/7a8442cfa4a6ab3e6369c2d4f6f96154_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic3.zhimg.com%2F50%2F7a8442cfa4a6ab3e6369c2d4f6f96154_hd.jpg&h=f50572fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f54b481ca3116c9968710a44347cd437e6ed2437","tid":1582124,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T01:59:06.000Z","msg":"[公海 文宣整合] 9.29全球反極權集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581746</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8om5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=05f2f47a\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8om5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=3026b91c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"87b6aa37a9f33ee6845f181596075645114acd2f","tid":1582124,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T01:59:17.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https